    "stage": "Stage 3 \u2014 Data Architecture",
    "description": "Game state schema for LUU cooperative card game. This defines every value the app must track during a live game. All IDs reference cards defined in luu-cards.json and luu-action-cards.json.",
    "notes": [
      "Designed for solo play first. Multiplayer extends the players array.",
      "All cardIds reference the id field in the card definition files.",
      "positions in Luu queue are 1-indexed (position 1 = front, takes damage first).",
      "Damage counters are tracked separately from maxHp so level-up scaling is clean.",
      "Active effects are stored globally and reference the Luu or player they are attached to."
    ]
  },
